data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 4 bed, 2.5 bath home sitting on nearly an acre lot! The spacious deck overlooking the oversized background is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying your morning coffee. The breezeway connecting the 2 car garage with the home doubles as a mud room and gives access to the newly stained deck. Natural light abounds on the main level, featuring large windows. This home offers a living room with a cozy gas fireplace, dining room, and kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances and new backsplash. There are four great sized bedrooms, one conveniently located on the main level along with an additional space used as an office or fifth bedroom. The remaining two bedrooms and a full bathroom are located on the upper level. A spacious walk-in closet is ready for your finishing touches. It doesn't stop there! Venture downstairs to the in-law suite with family room and kitchen. Just down the hall is a half bathroom and the fourth bedroom. Lower level walks out to the patio and fenced-in backyard. Notable updates include: new siding 2021, main level paint 2021. Don't miss your opportunity to own this amazing property! Schedule your private tour today!
